blogPost.excerpt:
I've dreamt of this day for as long as I can remember. In the midst of our darkest storm, God blessed us with our rainbow baby. 

We cannot thank you enough for your prayer and support throughout our fertility journey. This pregnancy is the greatest honor of my life, and I'm so thankful to be able to share this moment with you. 

Dreams really do come true.
